{"tid":1997101,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思廣益]比朋友背叛 如何自處","createTime":"2020-05-01T11:57:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-02T14:34:34.000Z","uid":50849,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"2ca396d925adf3574c6405378a6060e97bc12e9d","tid":1997101,"uid":50849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T11:57:07.000Z","msg":"你地有冇試過比朋友背叛 出賣自己？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n發現從頭到尾 都只係自己一霜情願當人好朋友<br />\n喺人地眼中，自己係可以隨時被捨棄 ...<br />\n<br />\n你地點樣可以走返出黎？ <br />\n依家我每日一諗起就會喊，覺得自己好蠢，好想死<br />\n嚴重到影響埋工作同生活，好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n應該點做好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9e81f4ed765636b8f1f05c04b9f53dc18424bc6","tid":1997101,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T11:58:02.000Z","msg":"C"},{"pid":"2346b3dbc09a0a6e08e5455fe0e3bddbc48401be","tid":1997101,"uid":299372,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T12:03:00.000Z","msg":"反省下點解會一廂情願, 對方冇回應你都繼續付出? <br />\n衰第一次不必自責, 小心下次唔好就夠<br />\n人就係咁成長"},{"pid":"c75000feda74ce69f0304960082293044cff280a","tid":1997101,"uid":97887,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T12:28:55.000Z","msg":"試過<br />\n<br />\n比同事/朋友背叛<br />\n<br />\n喺我面前擺可憐<br />\n<br />\n喺大家面前踩低我<br />\n<br />\n有事要我幫<br />\n<br />\n無事伸開我奚落我<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d0a6657f1329aff88341aa4612a757e815301e1","tid":1997101,"uid":50849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c75000feda74ce69f0304960082293044cff280a","tid":1997101,"uid":97887,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T12:28:55.000Z","msg":"試過<br />\n<br />\n比同事/朋友背叛<br />\n<br />\n喺我面前擺可憐<br />\n<br />\n喺大家面前踩低我<br />\n<br />\n有事要我幫<br />\n<br />\n無事伸開我奚落我<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.g